 detail as we progress.</span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt; font-family:=
&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">However, I do tru=
st that this will give you some insight and knowledge to allow us to partic=
ipate in the process together.</span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt; font-=
family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I look forward to=
 speaking with you soon.</span><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt; font-family=
:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Please confirm ba=
